<taxonomicName id="4DE707E0264C525CD6827D947B95F423" class="Polyplacophora" family="Chitonidae" genus="Radsia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Radsia barnesii" order="Chitonida" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="barnesii">Radsia barnesii</taxonomicName>
, Sur Playa Ramada, 22 mm; 3. 
<taxonomicName id="8E60B2BFC6DB008CDFAB30EE77D57014" class="Polyplacophora" family="Chitonidae" genus="Tonicia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tonicia atrata" order="Chitonida" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="atrata">Tonicia atrata</taxonomicName>
, Sur de Playa Brava, 30 mm; 4. 
<taxonomicName id="F3A27D9CB8332A664D31C00FE09F948F" class="Polyplacophora" family="Chitonidae" genus="Tonicia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tonicia chilensis" order="Chitonida" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="chilensis">Tonicia chilensis</taxonomicName>
, Playa Mansa, 32 mm. Scale bars are: 1 cm for 2 and 4, 2 cm for 3 and 4 cm for 1.
</paragraph>
